Package: kgroups
Type: Package
Title: K-Means Clustering with Automated Optimization and Quality Control
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Christophe Desterke
Maintainer: Christophe Desterke <christophe.desterke@gmail.com>
Description: Provides a streamlined workflow for k-means clustering, including 
    automated optimization of the number of clusters and comprehensive quality 
    control metrics. Each optimization step generates modern, publication-ready 
    visualizations using 'ggplot2'.
